title: Exile and You
author: suthrnpride44
pages:
#- The following actions are considered heinous and will be treated as pearlable offenses:§0
§0
§01. Killing of another player. This includes killing someone just for fun (it's just a prank bro). Sparring must be done on the DevPVP server to avoid accidents.
#- Killing in self defense is permitted, but the slayer must provide proof that the slayee was going to cause them harm. Without this proof the killer will be the one punished without question. Theft is not a valid reason to kill someone.§0
§0
§0Turn page --->
#- 2. Theft of personal property valued over 100 diamonds.§0
§0
§0Theft is considered taking something without permission, or in the case someone is offline, taking something and not letting that person know you borred it. Value of the stolen goods will be 
#- determined by an auditor. Enchanted gear may be audited at a high price depending on the enchant. Titanium and Platinum are valued at 3 diamond each. Obsidian is valued at 50 diamonds each. Iron, steel, aluminum, and silicon are valued at 1/2 diamonds ea.
#- *Note that these values are audited values for theft and do not reflect the value of items when it comes to trade.§0
§0
§03. Theft of or tresspassing on state property. §0
§0
§0Taking property from an agency of the state that you do not
#- work for is a pearlable offense. Tresspassing in areas off limits to the public will also result in exile. Please speak to someone within the agency you need to get in touch with, and if no one is on please let that agency know what was done.§0
§0
§0Next page  
#- 4. Raiding or Griefing another nation.§0
§0
§0Raiding and griefing brings unwanted attention to Little Richard Island and will not be tolerated.§0
§0
§05. Treason §0
§0
§0Giving away state secrets or information otherwise considered 
#- confidential will be considered treason. Aiding another nation in the invasion of Little Richard Island will result in exile. §0
§0
§06. Killing exessive amounts of domesticated animals. Killing pets.§0
§0
§0Killing a pet or killing all of one type of
#- animal will result in pearling. Animals are a luxury resource and are very very expensive to replace. Please don't kill animals unless you get permission from the correct agency.§0
§0
§07. Forgery of official documents.§0
§0
§0Forging/duplication 
#- of passports, printing plates, currency, or other official documents is a pearlable offense. Please contact the Printmeister if you wish to receive a copy of your passport or need a document duplicated.§0
§0

#- 